    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for MRL 2. CFD predictions demonstrate adequate agreement with FDA GCBP experimental hemolysis data. The 95th-percentile operating point yields RH = 0.97, satisfying the percentile-based acceptance requirement. The package is accepted for regulatory submission supporting the Class II CPB device 510(k) filing.",
